NAME
  graph_2_mat - node-arc incidence matrix from graph

CALLING SEQUENCE
  [a] = graph_2_mat(g)

PARAMETERS
  g : graph-list
  a : sparse node-arc incidence matrix

DESCRIPTION
  graph_2_mat computes the node-arc incidence matrix corresponding to the
  graph g.

EXAMPLE
  g=load_graph(SCI+'/demos/metanet/colored');
  a=graph_2_mat(g)

SEE ALSO
  mat_2_graph




































